title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – May 13 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – May 13 2022
description:
Pandemia author Alex Berenson joins Clay to analyze the latest on covid and free speech in America. What would the media do if Trump had presided over this covid disaster? OutKick's Bobby Burack talks woke sports with Clay. Netflix finally tells woke employees to quit if they're offended. Friday the 13th: What are your favorite scary movies?

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
